  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tablespoon of vegetable oil in a large pot over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the pork shoulder and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the Thai chilli jam, soy sauce, and rice vinegar, and stir to combine.",
    "Add 2 cups of water and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
